==English==
===Noun===
'''[[trigonometric]] [[function]]''' (''plural'' '''trigonometric functions''')

#{{trigonometry}} Any function of an [[angle]] expressed as the [[ratio]] of [[two]] of the [[side]]s of a [[right triangle]] that has that angle.

